query:
SELECT h.id, h.name, h.linkedDocumentId, d.id as docId, d.name as docName, d.fileUrl, d.mimeType
FROM hotels h
LEFT JOIN documents d ON h.linkedDocumentId = d.id
WHERE h.name LIKE '%Vienna%'
LIMIT 10;
